# CQ-2: What OTel attributes does each LIVE rule require?
PREFIX aat: <urn:ontostar:aat:live:>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?rule ?label ?attribute WHERE {
  ?rule a aat:LiveRule ;
        rdfs:label ?label ;
        aat:requiredAttribute ?attribute .
} ORDER BY ?label ?attribute
